{"tid":287713,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇東京近郊推介","createTime":"2017-06-17T15:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T08:10:06.000Z","uid":39195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df9ee7a62fe98a5372d4bcd20ebe244b196fcb84","tid":287713,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲可唔可以推介以下邊一個係我正地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 輕井澤<br />\n2. 日光<br />\n3. 箱根<br />\n4. 越後湯澤<br />\n5. 橫濱<br />\n6. 鐮倉<br />\n7. 江之島<br />\n8. 富士山河口湖<br />\n9. 高尾山<br />\n10. 川越<br />\n11. 秩父<br />\n12. 伊豆<br />\n13. 熱海<br />\n14. 三浦半島<br />\n15. 佐原"},{"pid":"7f3bcff9438f23eba67a9b2bdc94da57d15e8e25","tid":287713,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T18:23:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e57b175f940707b67158c175760ea6fe32483486","tid":287713,"uid":104745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T18:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴絲可唔可以推介以下邊一個係我正地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 輕井澤<br />\n2. 日光<br />\n3. 箱根<br />\n4. 越後湯澤<br />\n5. 橫濱<br />\n6. 鐮倉<br />\n7. 江之島<br />\n8. 富士山河口湖<br />\n9. 高尾山<br />\n10. 川越<br />\n11. 秩父<br />\n12. 伊豆<br />\n13. 熱海<br />\n14. 三浦半島<br />\n15. 佐原</blockquote><br />\n只去過3,5,6,7,8,10,12,13<br />\n6,7可以即日來回，覺得好正，每次去東京都會去走一轉<br />\n川越都係即日，行下舊街幾有特色影相唔錯<br />\n3,8,12,13可以住一晚溫泉旅館，睇下靚景relax下"},{"pid":"64f73bf8f17bba541673fc12042b41de678d3f8c","tid":287713,"uid":113483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T23:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴絲可唔可以推介以下邊一個係我正地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 輕井澤<br />\n2. 日光<br />\n3. 箱根<br />\n4. 越後湯澤<br />\n5. 橫濱<br />\n6. 鐮倉<br />\n7. 江之島<br />\n8. 富士山河口湖<br />\n9. 高尾山<br />\n10. 川越<br />\n11. 秩父<br />\n12. 伊豆<br />\n13. 熱海<br />\n14. 三浦半島<br />\n15. 佐原</blockquote><br />\n我去過 1，2，3，4，5，6，7，8，10，12<br />\n如果浸溫泉不如去日光<br />\n日光好多旅館幾百年歷史<br />\n日光無箱根咁商業<br />\n<br />\n鐮倉主要睇佛<br />\n不過而家d人主要去睇條平交道<br />\n<br />\n川越d神社/廟都幾有特色<br />\n我個陣撞正有祭典<br />\n好熱鬧<br />\n<br />\n越後湯澤有個清酒博物館<br />\n可以一去"},{"pid":"6abc4b724e00326992e1cb9c884229770cfceea7","tid":287713,"uid":33065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T00:10:02.000Z","msg":"咁多個我覺得高尾山最正<br />\n上次全程行上去遇到好多當地人都好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5249bcb3ec9315be3b4100b7099db859f164dd","tid":287713,"uid":39195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T01:07:51.000Z","msg":"多謝各巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30afea5e49661333f37161292624cc5838aebb86","tid":287713,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a122913f22d180400972ae9088156d6cdd154d","tid":287713,"uid":5172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"佐原好撚正"},{"pid":"ab4e0d247fdfc4ec57bc7c93baa749ea5df88f48","tid":287713,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佐原好撚正</blockquote><br />\n風景靚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4a806a553d4936a78b7b49942268fdffe07450","tid":287713,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"川越真係嘥氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條街古就古 行半個鐘就完<br />\n去左個神社 都係好細 10分鐘"},{"pid":"c9ae23769c6d7b79504baecc99b7206263958007","tid":287713,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"千葉濃溝瀑布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d452d88214467d59c3d0f3c5bbcb7fbc50249d8b","tid":287713,"uid":81751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T1