score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"房總半島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eab1df877d0dcac08665080fa5d5a31d5535a9","tid":287713,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過那須同輕井澤。前者就去親近下啲動物同大自然，後者就好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果遲d 8月有9日,東京去輕井澤富山金澤落名古屋可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果去埋合掌村點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}